data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom home is a true gem, boasting not one but 2 master bedrooms, three well-appointed bathrooms, and a two-car garage. The yard boasts a generous inground pool with a covered patio, offering ample outdoor space for enjoyment. As you step inside, the inviting open layout welcomes you, featuring a spacious living room with a sliding glass door that provides effortless access to the yard, offering plenty of space for relaxation and enjoyment. The chef's dream kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances. The property is enclosed by a beautifully wrought iron fence with an electric gate at the front, providing an air of elegance and security. In the backyard, a 5-6-foot wooden fence adds privacy and charm, making this home a perfect blend of style and comfort. Conveniently located, to schools, shopping centers, and other entertainment. Don't miss this opportunity!
